Description
==================================================
	Main program is ParticlesSystem.cpp

	Usage: ./ParticlesSystem [parameters-file]	

	Read parameters from file parameters.
	Use key 'S' to start.
	Use key 'q' to quit.
	Use key 'l' to enable light. // do_light() function is from the class material of CPSC6050 by Geist
	Use mouse to toggle view point.
